Package rr.simple

Class Summary
CountTool Count the number of events for most common cases.
EmptyTool Like LastTool, but keeps ShadowVar set to thread, so that the fast path in the Instrumenter is triggered.
LastTool The last tool in any tool chain.
MethodMonitoringTool Super class that adds a decoration to each method indicating whether or not it is "interesting".
PrintTool Print a human readable event stream.
SyncTool Synchronize all event handling.
ThreadLocalTool Identifies thread local accesses and filters them out.
